repos/dali-ui/dali-ui-foundation/integration-api/text-visualizer/docs/15-current-optimization-status.ko.md:386:- `SetText()` / `SetFontFamily()` / `SetFontSize()`는 prepare + layout + render dirty를 다시 set한다.
